1781093393763160	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy3RI		item.comment	bn-8zqz	{"body":"Merged to main fc0dd397: new workspace::conflict_state is the single source of truth for merge gate, ws conflicts, resolve --list, lifecycle/status/list/diff/destroy-preview; stale sidecars auto-clear on first read after a manual resolution commit (no follow-up sync); bn-28d1 placeholder tripwire kept non-bypassable. Combined just check green."}	blake3:TiN-exMZWg8S_NL5G5zahRnN3-QGeCtQDOMgGwGbu7A
